    <item>
      <title>热力学第二定律的统计意义和熵的概念</title>
      <link>https://circlecirclezero.cc/2022/05/06/%E7%83%AD%E5%8A%9B%E5%AD%A6%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E5%AE%9A%E5%BE%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1%E6%84%8F%E4%B9%89%E5%92%8C%E7%86%B5%E7%9A%84%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5/</link>
      <guid>https://circlecirclezero.cc/2022/05/06/%E7%83%AD%E5%8A%9B%E5%AD%A6%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E5%AE%9A%E5%BE%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1%E6%84%8F%E4%B9%89%E5%92%8C%E7%86%B5%E7%9A%84%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 May 2022 06:27:48 GMT</pubDate>
      
        
        
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&quot;克劳修斯熵&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#克劳修斯熵&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;克劳修斯熵&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;克劳修斯熵&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;卡诺定理&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;工作在两确定的热源之间的一切&lt;strong&gt;可逆机&lt;/strong&gt;的效率相等&lt;</description>
        
      
      
      
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h1 id="克劳修斯熵"><a href="#克劳修斯熵" class="headerlink" title="克劳修斯熵"></a>克劳修斯熵</h1><p>卡诺定理</p><ul><li>工作在两确定的热源之间的一切<strong>可逆机</strong>的效率相等<ul><li>$\displaystyle \eta_{\text{可}} = 1 - \frac{T_2}{T_1}$</li></ul></li><li>一切<strong>不可逆机</strong>的效率小于可逆热机的效率<ul><li>$\displaystyle \eta_{\text{不可}} &lt; 1 - \frac{T_2}{T_1}$</li></ul></li></ul><p>对可逆卡诺循环</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\begin{aligned} \frac{Q_1}{T_1} = \frac{\left\vert Q_2 \right\vert }{T_2}\\ \frac{Q_1}{T_1}+\frac{Q_2}{T_2}=0\end{aligned}</script><p>任意一个可逆循环，都可以看成由无数( $N$ )个卡诺循环所组成<br>对其中第 i 个有: $\displaystyle \frac{Q_{1i}}{T_{1i}} + \frac{Q_{2i}}{T_{2i}} = 0$</p><p>对N个卡诺循环: $\displaystyle \sum_{i=1}^{2N} \frac{Q_i}{T_i} = 0$</p><p>克劳修斯等式( $T$ 是热源温度):</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\begin{equation}\lim_{N \to \infty} \sum_{i=1}^{2N} \frac{Q_i}{T_i} =0  \\\end{equation}</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\begin{equation}    \oint \frac{\mathrm{d}Q}{T} =0\end{equation}</script><h2 id="熵的定义"><a href="#熵的定义" class="headerlink" title="熵的定义"></a>熵的定义</h2><img data-src="/2022/05/06/%E7%83%AD%E5%8A%9B%E5%AD%A6%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E5%AE%9A%E5%BE%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1%E6%84%8F%E4%B9%89%E5%92%8C%E7%86%B5%E7%9A%84%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5/2022-05-06-17-23-18.png" class=""><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\int_{L_1} \frac{\mathrm{d}Q}{\mathrm{d}T_{2}} \frac{\mathrm{d}Q}{\mathrm{d}T} =\cdots =\int_{AB} \frac{\mathrm{d}Q}{\mathrm{d}T}</script><ul><li>积分值只由初末态决定，与积分路径无关</li></ul><p>一定存在一个态函数,它的增量只与状态有关，而与变化的路径无关。</p><ul><li>态函数“<strong>熵</strong>”,记为 “$S$”</li></ul><p>克劳修斯熵公式</p><p>“熵”的定义式（对可逆过程）</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">S_{B} - S_{A} = \int_{A}^{B} \frac{\mathrm{d}Q}{\mathrm{d}T}</script><ul><li>$S_A$: 初态的熵</li><li>$S_B$: 末态的熵</li></ul><p>对无限小的可逆过程</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\mathrm{d}S = \frac{\mathrm{d}Q}{T}</script><script type="text&#x2F;javascript" src="https://unpkg.com/kity@2.0.4/dist/kity.min.js"></script><script type="text&#x2F;javascript" src="https://unpkg.com/kityminder-core@1.4.50/dist/kityminder.core.min.js"></script><script defer="true" type="text&#x2F;javascript" src="https://unpkg.com/hexo-simple-mindmap@0.8.0/dist/mindmap.min.js"></script><link rel="stylesheet" type="text&#x2F;css" href="https://unpkg.com/hexo-simple-mindmap@0.8.0/dist/mindmap.min.css">]]></content:encoded>
      
      
